  "title": "Senior Delivery Lead",
  "description": "<p>The Senior Delivery Lead will be accountable for delivering the following:</p><p>•\tPre-study deliverables defined by client</p><p>•\tProgram Governance Process Compliance</p><p>•\tResource & Financial Management</p><p>•\tComprehensive Status Reporting & Program Dashboards: Regular, transparent, and data-driven reporting on program health, including progress against plan, budget variance, resource utilization, and risk/issues status.</p><p>Qualifications & Experience</p><p>•\tRequired:</p><p>o\tBachelor’s or master’s degree in computer science, engineering, business administration, or a related field.</p><p>o\t12-15+ years of experience in technology program and project management, with a proven track record of successfully delivering large-scale, complex, multi-year initiatives.</p><p>o\tMinimum of 7 years of experience within the Banking and Financial Services industry, with a strong understanding of Trade/Lending/Payment/CASA.</p><p>o\tDemonstrable experience managing large-scale transformation programs</p><p>o\tExpert-level knowledge of formal SDLC and project management methodologies (e.g., Waterfall, Agile, Hybrid).</p><p>o\tExperience managing program budgets in excess of $10M.</p><p>o\tExcellent communication skills with all stakeholders.</p><p>o\tHands-on experience in managing resources in multiple locations</p><p>o\tProven strong leadership</p>",
